         <abstract id="aspace_906bd94bdc8a2973bfed6da9d92d0753">The records consist of correspondence, reports, course descriptions, financial records, and personnel files documenting the Signal Corps School for Officer Candidates at Yale.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
